	<span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;
          letter-spacing:.05pt"><span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. определя броя и </span><span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:
          .3pt">избира<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>и<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>освобождава<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>членовете<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>на<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>Управителния<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>съвет<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>и<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>определя </span><span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;">възнаграждението им;<i><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></i></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;
   line-height:150%;">
	<span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;
          letter-spacing:-.1pt">3. приема <span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>отчета за дейността на Управителния съвет;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;
   ">
	<span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;
          letter-spacing:.1pt">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4. </span><span lang="BG" style="font-family:Arial;
